org.eclipse.scada.vi.model

Interface GridContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Container, Primitive
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GridContainerImpl

    public interface GridContainer
extends Container
    A representation of the model object 'Grid Container'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Columns
    • Equal Width
    • Children
    • Horizontal Spacing
    • Vertical Spacing
    • Margin Width
    • Margin Height

    See Also:
    VisualInterfacePackage.getGridContainer()
